node_7.subject: Isabella Rodriguez
node_7.description: This is Isabella Rodriguez's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 8:00 am, read a paper and take notes at 9:00 am, prepare her presentation on the paper at 10:00 am, give her presentation to a group of people she has arranged to meet at 11:00 am, have a lunch break at 12:30 pm, engage in conversations with the people she met about the paper they have all read at 1:30 pm, continue networking and discussing ideas with others at 2:30 pm, take some time for herself to relax and recharge at 4:00 pm.
